{"tid":1924561,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"支衛：歐洲成為中國冠狀病毒大流行的中心","createTime":"2020-03-13T18:02:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-13T18:52:58.000Z","uid":21470,"like":3,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"5d6b11553a5c6b35ff8c6f6b942ca464ec907075","tid":1924561,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T18:02:10.000Z","msg":"譚德塞：歐洲成為新型冠狀病毒大流行的中心<br />\n<br />\n世衛組織總幹事譚德塞表示，隨著歐洲每日確診新型冠狀病毒個案的數量比中國多，認為歐洲已經成為病毒大流行的中心。他重申每個國家都要綜合措施抗疫，需要將測試、追踪、隔離、減少社交一起做，如果認為自己的國家不會出現疫情，將會是一個致命錯誤。<br />\n<br />\n對於在伊朗有過萬宗確診病例，世衛官員指，伊朗在遏制疫情正朝著正確方向發展，但仍要做更多工作，又指世衛仍在研究這種新病毒。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1273537&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1273537%26csid%3D261_341&d=B95HL5QQ1MLE%2FldfuzA7j2o8q5%2FbnpuKyKF%2Fs7IAglk%3D&h=5209d145\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1273537&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"851892755a97ed50ccaa581ff673eb44c8142393","tid":1924561,"uid":41389,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T18:03:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />繼續火上加油 遲早WHO比人燒"},{"pid":"8693815cf4406552afd8541140f422d38f619e74","tid":1924561,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T18:05:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86a68fb09edcd984a301290093b14805273747f2","tid":1924561,"uid":258649,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T18:05:23.000Z","msg":"又係你話封關太過敏感既，咁咪大家唔封關攬炒lo<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\